{"tid":2139175,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"但你人都未到，個設施已經正式啟用，仲點樣「協助建」呢？ #亞博治療中心","createTime":"2020-08-04T06:22:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T06:22:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9055d3dac40d8c83d95c7364572bbb6e4eff82ed","tid":2139175,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"但你人都未到，個設施已經正式啟用，仲點樣「協助建」呢？<br />\n#亞博治療中心<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/WG5ZJGWSV3LECIALQZ5YNVVBZY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FWG5ZJGWSV3LECIALQZ5YNVVBZY%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4YdxUAsmJrpgm%2FsQZzOZZuI0I%3D&h=04da96b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FWG5ZJGWSV3LECIALQZ5YNVVBZY%2F&h=117331d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/WG5ZJGWSV3LECIALQZ5YNVVBZY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【李八方online】港自建亞博治療中心被大陸邀功 彭博疑照抄央視fake news捱轟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gXVL66j7Z1VVaHECwGncWS5b3Ko=/639x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4AE4HA5VK36CKCG4H4O5HUOQZE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgXVL66j7Z1VVaHECwGncWS5b3Ko%3D%2F639x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4AE4HA5VK36CKCG4H4O5HUOQZE.png&h=8f88f2f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n8月1日啟用嘅機場亞洲博覽館「社區治療設施」，明明係香港醫管局一手一腳改建，居然俾大陸邀功，辣㷫好多人。公立醫院醫生鄺葆賢都忍唔住出post澄清，認為唔應該連呢個「credit都要雙手送人」。<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。話說中共官媒央視CCTV話，大陸派人嚟香港「協助建方艙」，為改建亞博「提供設計、營運及管理經驗」喎；大陸衞生健康委都有類似講法。<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">但你人都未到，個設施已經正式啟用，仲點樣「協助建」呢？</span></span>之前被爆親中嘅彭博通訊社，竟然完全照抄央視同衞健委一面之辭，仲大字標題話「中國幫香港建臨時醫院（China to Help Hong Kong Build Mobile Hospital）」，激到大批網民鬧爆佢寫fake news呀。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：彭博通訊社親中 涉逼前記者簽保密協議<br />\n<br />\n本身係公立醫院醫生嘅黃埔區區議員鄺葆賢都忍唔住出post，澄清返亞博館個場係由醫管局一班同事搭出嚟，認為唔應該連呢個「credit都要雙手送人」，仲叫大家唔好再嗌亞博館做方艙醫院啊，「要叫就叫番本名：『社區治療設施』」，即係亞博社區治療設施。睇返醫管局個page，喺7月31嗰陣已經出post話，喺醫管局前線同後勤人員嘅努力下，社區治療設施嘅籌組同建設就即將完成，為正式啟用做好準備，然後8月1號就正式啟用。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭同張建宗前幾日話，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n面對網民排山倒海留言表達不滿，被指親中嘅彭博通訊社喺篇報道同帖文出街後，直至第3日嘅凌晨仍然未有回應；而篇報道同帖文亦都未見修正。<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n打國際線 《蘋果》英文版免費試睇 按此了解更多<br />\n英文版已登錄新版《蘋果》App按此下載/更新<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/j88iGe_F4Ma8l874-Iv5z04outQ=/640x453/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JHSIZMZDTTXELYW23LUTYCNHRY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fj88iGe_F4Ma8l874-Iv5z04outQ%3D%2F640x453%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJHSIZMZDTTXELYW23LUTYCNHRY.png&h=3ae049f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中共官媒央視CCTV話，派6個武漢專家嚟香港「協助建方艙」，為改建亞博「提供設計、營運及管理經驗」喎。但你人都未到，個設施已經正式啟用，仲點樣「協助建」呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KqatlDwugqjuGi6nuY1HcgMaml8=/640x544/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A4S2FUREX3FADC2AO2NIN2D5BE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKqatlDwugqjuGi6nuY1HcgMaml8%3D%2F640x544%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA4S2FUREX3FADC2AO2NIN2D5BE.png&h=f63d68d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大陸衞生健康委亦都話大陸派6個武漢專家嚟香港，為改建亞博做「方艙醫院」「提供設計、營運及管理經驗」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bRkGk2bKVDHf_eLU4eAdfTbcHIM=/639x503/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TZFJZGUETOYIAFSDFOP3FXWGE4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbRkGk2bKVDHf_eLU4eAdfTbcHIM%3D%2F639x503%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTZFJZGUETOYIAFSDFOP3FXWGE4.png&h=ec978841&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前被爆親中嘅彭博通訊社，竟然完全照抄大陸衞健委同央視一面之辭，仲大字標題話「中國幫香港起臨時醫院（China to Help Hong Kong Build Mobile Hospital）」，激到大批網民去佢Facebook鬧爆佢寫fake news。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hQoEvOs5IZohRM2vrg5A2JMjajc=/640x1094/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CJYI3ZBSMNOUGOQSZJHMO2Q5QA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhQoEvOs5IZohRM2vrg5A2JMjajc%3D%2F640x1094%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCJYI3ZBSMNOUGOQSZJHMO2Q5QA.png&h=dbe44080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批網民忍唔住去Bloomberg Asia嘅Facebook page度留言，話亞博嘅改建係由香港醫管局去做，中國係無幫過手㗎，仲鬧佢哋呢個報道好誤導啊。"}]}